\f0\fs24 \cf0 # \uc0\u55357 \u56520  Programming Language Trends (Stack Overflow Data)\
\
This project visualizes the popularity of various programming languages over time using Stack Overflow post data. It uses **Pandas** for data manipulation and **Matplotlib** for data visualization. To smooth out short-term fluctuations and highlight longer-term trends, the chart uses a **rolling mean**.\
\
---\
\
## \uc0\u55357 \u56589  Objective\
\
To analyze time-series data and visualize trends in programming language popularity by:\
\
- Importing and transforming CSV data\
- Reshaping the dataset for multi-line plotting\
- Applying a **rolling average** for better trend analysis\
- Creating a clean, informative chart with labels and legends\
\
---\
\
## \uc0\u55357 \u56522  Example Output\
\
The chart displays a smoothed line graph for each programming language, showing the number of related Stack Overflow posts over time. Smoothing is achieved using a 6-month rolling mean.\
\
