\
## \uc0\u55357 \u56513  Dataset\
\
The data comes from a CSV file named `QueryResults.csv` with the following columns:\
\
- `DATE`: Monthly timestamp\
- `TAG`: Programming language name (e.g., Python, Java)\
- `POSTS`: Number of Stack Overflow posts for that language\
